heating means define the air temperature which is in a fuel-air ratio close to the stoichiometric &#x394;=1, stabilizing means define the automatic control of the system by regulating the air and fuel flow. The biomass to be used as fuel in the present invention must be of millimetric size and the humidity content must not be greater than 30%. It can be used any kind of dry matter of vegetable or peat of different calorific power. The heat generated may be used in all conventional techniques.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>